title: Shahid talks about his pride in being Pakistani American

media:group.media:title: Shahid talks about his pride in being Pakistani American
media:group.media:description:
Shahid, a “Being Asian in America” documentary participant, talks about the pride he feels being Pakistani American and how he’s been able to make his dreams come true in the U.S.

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
